{'text': 'If you truly are addicted to drugs, you should be treated like an addict, not a criminal.'}
{'text': 'If we legalize drugs, what will happen to the drug cartels? Will they be driven out of business?'}
{'text': "2. I don't want to see an increase in overdoses. I want to see a decrease in overdoses."}
{'text': "Why are we not able to control the distribution of alcohol, tobacco, and pharmaceuticals? Why isn't the government able to control these things?"}
{'text': "Think of the thousands of kids just like your friend who aren't using drugs. Think of the many lives that are ruined by the use of drugs."}
{'text': 'If drugs are legalized, the government should not have the power to imprison people for drug-related crimes.'}
{'text': "I think that it is ridiculous that we can't have a national discussion about the merits and demerits of legalization. There are so many things that we could learn from such a discussion."}
